# VENDOR EVERYTHING EXCEPT C# TO FORCE A C# ONLY COUNT

# 1. EXPLICITLY COUNT C#
*.cs linguist-language=C#

# 2. VENDOR/IGNORE ALL OTHER COMMON UNITY FILES
# This will exclude assets, configuration, and shader code.
*.mat linguist-vendored
*.asset linguist-vendored
*.prefab linguist-vendored
*.unity linguist-vendored
*.meta linguist-vendored
*.json linguist-vendored
*.asmdef linguist-vendored
*.txt linguist-vendored
*.md linguist-vendored
*.xml linguist-vendored
*.html linguist-vendored

# 3. VENDOR ALL SHADER/GRAPHICS FILES
*.shader linguist-vendored
*.hlsl linguist-vendored
*.cginc linguist-vendored

# 4. VENDOR COMMON IMAGE/AUDIO FILES (Optional but helpful)
# If you have large PNGs, this ensures the size doesn't skew the results
*.png linguist-vendored
*.jpg linguist-vendored
*.ogg linguist-vendored
*.mp3 linguist-vendored
*.wav linguist-vendored
*.sprite linguist-vendored